snippet.title: CodePlanStudio
snippet.description:
If you want to make your own game and publish to the wide audience. This channel is for you.

My channel is all about teaching you how to create games. 
You will learn how to publish and monetize your game by displaying advertisements and using in app purchases. 

So, if you want to become game developer or learn how to make your own mobile game and publish it to the Google Play Store or IOS App Store, make sure to subscribe to my channel right now. 

As you can see my channel publishes video that focus on the game development. We will make many great games together. 
I will guide you step by step, in developing your mobile game and monetize it, so you can generate some side income from your passion.

If this sounds like something that could help you in your game development journey, than make sure to join me by subscribing!
